data.description: Welcome to this 1949 Parade of Homes charmer! Enter into a large living room with a wood burning fireplace and attached dining room - both have professionally finished hardwood floors. The updated kitchen has stainless steel appliances and a breakfast nook. The two car garage is attached by a breezeway protecting you from snow and rain and doubles as a cozy enclosed porch.  The basement boasts a large family room with knotty cedar walls, a wood burning fireplace and a dry bar.   The house needs a little TLC and a new family to make it their home.
